</header><article class="story story-blogpost"><a id="mainContent"></a><div class="storytitle">
      <h1>Airbnb, New York State Spar Over Legality Of Rentals</h1>
   <input type="hidden" id="title356728035" value="Airbnb, New York State Spar Over Legality Of Rentals" />
