                        <a id="featuredStackSquareImage304564169" href="https://www.npr.org/sections/alltechconsidered/2014/04/18/304564169/airbnb-to-start-charging-hotel-taxes-in-a-handful-of-cities"  data-metrics='{"category":"Story to Story","action":"Click Internal Link","label":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/sections\/alltechconsidered\/2014\/04\/18\/304564169\/airbnb-to-start-charging-hotel-taxes-in-a-handful-of-cities"}' ><img src="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2014/04/18/airbnb_sq-6d645d80f2b9bf500aa93775915a4fda057e53c6-s100-c15.jpg" data-original="https://media.npr.org/assets/img/2014/04/18/airbnb_sq-6d645d80f2b9bf500aa93775915a4fda057e53c6-s100.jpg" class="img lazyOnLoad"  alt="Airbnb To Start Charging Hotel Taxes In A Handful Of Cities" /></a>            <div class="bucketblock">
